  25 Mar 2003; Joshua Brindle <method@gentoo.org> selinux-small-2003011510-r2.ebuild:
  changed to stable

  21 Mar 2003; Joshua Brindle <method@gentoo.org> selinux-small-2003011510-r2.ebuild,
